{"tid":1984381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫dse考生打氣 正面拆解「手足畀狗掟落街 你仲有心情考試？」","createTime":"2020-04-22T12:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T10:36:19.000Z","uid":201604,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d12d0696faabe96fe32ee93a0e7d916e1332636a","tid":1984381,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"相信呢幾日 五毛會用以下標題黎開post<br />\n「仲得閒/有心情溫書？」<br />\n「對唔對得住手足？」<br />\n「做咩唔罷考 仲跟制度玩？」<br />\n<br />\n光復香港唔係一朝一夕既事<br />\n你問下自己 有冇盡自己能力去做每一件事幫手<br />\n同時提升自己既能力同影響力<br />\n<br />\n前排有個post話 中共開始滲透大專校園<br />\n但我想講 好多年前已經開始左滲透<br />\n第時既大專學生會係本土派定奶共派 <br />\n係由你地決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷考只會益左藍絲<br />\n今屆考生 因為抗爭 <br />\n然後又武漢肺炎搞到延期 打亂晒大家計劃<br />\n可能你已經覺得好頹<br />\n但我都希望你地專注返考dse<br />\n努力埋佢就會好好多架啦<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己付出得唔夠既<br />\n唔通你驚考完試 抗爭就完左咩 一定唔會<br />\n呢段時間就等我地代你地操心<br />\n將來會更加需要你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲睇緊呢個post既你<br />\n係時候放低電話 拎返起本書<br />\n溫到攰就去休息下娛樂下 收拾下心情<br />\n大家都會支持你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84baa552656432b107dbdc1ff409b5a2e2ffcd20","tid":1984381,"uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"咁都有人鬥<br />\n我真係唔相信背後無人搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2592898d7852544cf9ce8ffe70dd12c812afdb","tid":1984381,"uid":244329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f842fa1fc5dca71a3bc2da152fa032707250c64f","tid":1984381,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,